I also found [a different solution](http://gee.cs.oswego.edu/dl/classes/EDU/oswego/cs/dl/util/concurrent/WaitFreeQueue.java) but the main problem with this code is that it uses `synchronized`, even though it&#39;s only doing so to simulate a CAS operation.

